<title>mjrwḥ ʿsẖạny</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- (mjrwḥ ʿlsẖạny .. dmh fdạny
 mdywn bʿmry .. ạ̉kẖḍʿ ạ̹lyh)2
 1- (wdywn ạlkẖṭyẗ .. wfạhạ ạlḥbyb
 dy nʿmẗ gẖnyẗ .. bạnt ʿ ạlṣlyb)2
 2- (wbmwth ạlkfạry .. ṣạlḥny mʿ ạlậb
 fy ạldm ạ̹ntṣạry .. wʿbwr ạlạ̉bwạb)2
 3- (wstr ʿywby .. nsạny ạlạ̉ḥzạn
 wgẖfr dẖnwby .. wṭwạhạ ạlnsyạn)2
 4- (wbṣwth ndạny .. mn wsṭ ạlạ̉sẖrạr
 ṭhrny wʿzạny .. hw yswʿ ạlbạr)2</lyrics>
</song>